1068086","type":"question","created":1720431482,"answer_count":164,"follower_count":306,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[215,5582,21438,2074658,3360343],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"小尹和小梁（均为化名）是姐弟关系，同住在一起。一日，小梁擅自拿走姐姐放置在客厅的车钥匙，并驾车外出。期间发生交通事故，造成一行人身亡。交警部门认定小梁全责。死者家属遂向法院提起诉讼，要求肇事者小梁赔偿损失，车主小尹承担连带赔偿责任。对此，小尹辩称，她对弟弟擅自拿车钥匙驾车外出并不知情，不应担责。广东江门新会法院审理认为，小尹作为肇事车辆的所有人，在明知同住的弟弟没有驾驶资格的情况下，随意将肇事车辆的钥匙放在客厅，未尽到妥善保管的义务，在保管车辆上存在过错。因此，法院酌定对超出交强险赔偿限额的损失为95万余元，由小尹承担30%的赔偿责任，由小梁承担70%的赔偿责任。 文/记者：章程 来源：广州日报车钥匙要保管好！弟弟偷开姐姐车撞死人姐姐担责三成_赔偿_车辆_肇事者"},"attached_info":"CkAI1v6k1fupj/hNEAMaCTEwOTE4MTYwNCD65q60BjAAOLICQAdyCTY2MTA2ODA4NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"168 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d1dd766fb20cdc63bbc137e3d8f915da_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1720682215.610701","card_id":"Q_21088829","target":{"id":21088829,"title":"英语里怎么表达「甲乙丙丁」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/21088829","type":"question","created":1369117741,"answer_count":41,"follower_count":266,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1100,12205],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CjwI1v6k1fupj/hNEAMaBjYxNjE0MCCtqOyMBTAAOIoCQAhyCDIxMDg4ODI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"140 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-80b7504862c733d3aa076784666c1edb_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1720682215.611000","card_id":"Q_660160451","target":{"id":660160451,"title":"能否拍下一张你认为最能代表中国传统美学特色的照片？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/660160451","type":"question","created":1719544760,"answer_count":201,"f